title: Lone Ranger TV Show Eps 01-06
description:
This is the first 6 episodes from the TV show that started in 1949 starring Clayton Moore and Jay Silverheels. I ripped these from a DVD collection I have but since I am new to this I don't know how to assess the quality. Due to my learning curve, some of the early episodes are avi. some are mp4 and a couple are even wmv. Fortunately I figured out what I was doing and started ripping them all in the same format (mp4) but that won't be until a few episodes down the road which I will post later.

If you have any questions just leave it in the comments, and I hope you enjoy...






Side note, I enjoyed the movie and recommend giving it a chance if you haven't seen it.
